#: org.kde.tasks.metainfo.xml:14
msgid ""
"Tasks is a to-do application. You can add, edit, and delete tasks and Tasks "
"will save your changes automatically. Tasks works on desktop and mobile."
msgstr ""
"Tasks je aplikacija za opravila. Opravila lahko dodajate, urejate in "
"brišete, Tasks pa bo vaše spremembe samodejno shranila. Tasks deluje na "
"namizju in mobilni napravi."

